text: KDOT (map legend) Sullivans Tracks is an unincorporated community in Grant County, Kansas, United States. It lies on the border of Sherman and Sullivan TownshipsCensus Bureau map, combined with county map at the intersection of the Cimarron Valley Railroad with Roads E and 13, 6 miles (9 km) west- southwest of the county seat of Ulysses.Official county map ==References== ==Further reading== ==External links== * Grant County Maps: Current, Historic, KDOT * Category:Unincorporated communities in Grant County, Kansas Category:Unincorporated communities in Kansas
